title: Mathieu van der Poel’s Team Alpecin-Deceuninck Partners Ketone Supplier for Performance Gains
content:
Belgian squad partners 'revolutionary ketone ester' supplier deltaG as nutritional supplement becomes less taboo in pro cycling.

Read the full article at Mathieu van der Poel’s Team Alpecin-Deceuninck Partners Ketone Supplier for Performance Gains on Velo.
author: Jim Cotton
